    "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
    "body": "> Consistency with every other game on the market sounds like one\r\n\r\nThis is primarily in single player games when the match is usually paused from entering the menus. Most multiplayer games display warnings when in menus since in MP your attention is actually needed. This is the same for FPS and RTS games.\r\n\r\nI feel most game designers would avoid the circumstance of someone dying in the menus without actually having any feedback. That said, Unit Lost is still heard through this, there is just no other warnings from what I can tell."
  },
