    "created_at": "2017-06-08T14:31:08Z",
    "updated_at": "2017-06-08T14:31:08Z",
    "author_association": "MEMBER",
    "body": "> In multiplayer, where it doesn't pause when the menu is opened, I think that all sounds should continue playing. \r\n\r\nMaking this work properly (without bugs like exactly this one) would require redesigning the way our UI code works, making it uglier and harder to maintain.  Muting sounds with the menu was just as much a technical decision as a UI consistency one."
